Sept. 22, 1990 D Fife Charities Band Association Contest
Fife Charities Band Association Contest 1 March, Hymn and Own Choice Test Piece Contest (Separate Points) Fife Charities Band Association Contest fife-charities-band-association-contest

Carnegie Hall, Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland, UK Open Contest Champions, best hymn and best march - Newmilns & Galston FCBA 'A Band' Champions: Cowdenbeath FCBA 'B Band' Champions: Buckhaven & Methil. Best section 2 band - Campbeltown. Best section 3 band - Perthshire Brass. Best section 4 band - Buckhaven and Methil. Only 6 bands competed. 45th annual contest.
